{"id": 2725, "genre": 1000, "title": "上网时你都有哪些“被迫形成”的习惯？", "description": "为了不踩网上的那些坑，我都把自己逼出习惯性强迫症了。（图片来自：iStock ©️ bobmadbob）", "record_count": 14414, "comment_count": 28, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190107175958y1uHlf2SEKb8kx7V.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-01-14T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5194, "title": "上网时你都有哪些“被迫形成”的习惯？", "content": "上网时你都有哪些“被迫形成”的习惯？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 321363, "content": "用搜索引擎搜“XX官网”，点开之前一定要先确认网址", "image": "img/option/option/20190107190132AdwigZSHr01vFMLC.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 321364, "content": "装了新 app，一定要检查一遍它都用了哪些手机权限", "image": "img/option/option/20190107190059jtrZv0QLiCbSfucV.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 321366, "content": "看评分先搜一星差评，自动跳过那些超长五星彩虹屁", "image": "img/option/option/20190109104724LmFvOEtTM2nUZKVa.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 321367, "content": "看到微博上的杠精，就算跟自己没交集也会预防性拉黑", "image": "img/option/option/20190107185935BkQmRfoglXtreFAj.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 321370, "content": "点开微信语音前，顺手先把手机音量调到不能更小", "image": "img/option/option/20190107190510HLniPywsevBMqojV.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 321373, "content": "看热搜话题的时候，习惯从第二个/第三个开始看起", "image": "img/option/option/20190107185855AIwKBybU1R9fo7Gx.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 321374, "content": "逛知乎的时候直接跳过“如何看待/如何评价xxx”类问题", "image": "img/option/option/20190107185848qbZpJNhiXe4Swndv.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 321380, "content": "过去从来不看的用户隐私政策，现在会认真过一遍再点", "image": "img/option/option/2019010718583827FR8yNpVxIPzv3L.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}